@startuml
title init sequence
box "Other threads" #lightgreen
participant  "CommonAPIProxyImpl" as Impl
'eventBuffer 에서 데이터도 같이 가지고 있어야 되는지 아니면 노티만 처리해야 되는지 확인 필요
'데이터를 가지고 있어야 싱크가 맞을거같음 혹은 데이터 아이디 만들기
participant  "eventBuffer" as event
endbox
box "GUI Thread" #lightblue
participant  "MainWindow" as MainWindow
participant  "OpenGLDrawClass" as GL
endbox

...
MainWindow -> GL : init()
GL -> GL : setState (NONE)

rnote over GL
  texture image setting
endrnote

rnote over GL
  shader setting
endrnote

event <-- GL : signal connect( requestDraw)

GL -> GL : setState (READY)
GL -> MainWindow
...


Impl -> event : init()

event -> event : init()
rnote over event
  currentData(DataContainerClass(NULL))
endrnote
rnote over event
  nextData(DataContainerClass(NULL))
endrnote

event --> GL : signal connect(setState)



event -> Impl : init finish



@enduml
